data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful one family home located at 9 Kuna Terrace, Upper Irvington. 3 BRS/MSTR BR with skylights, beautiful deck located off the 3rd bedroom. Eat in kitchen, Living-room with fire place. dining-room, sunroom, 3 bathrooms, and lots of closet space. A nice size yard, and so much more! Surrounding towns are Union and Maplewood!! Close to public transportation. Easy access to 78, GSPKWY and the Turnpike. (2.4) miles to Maplewood train station , (3.1) miles to Union train station. Home is being sold as-is. Home inspection for buyers informational purpose only. No known issues.Home is being delivered vacant! . Refrigerator, dishwasher, washer and dryer not included in the sale of the home
